                        <interp inst="t18790331-name-30" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD HEARN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Re-examined</hi>). There were some papers there like these (<hi rend="italic">printed circulars produced</hi>)—what I have here I got from a cupboard in his room—there are seven here.</p>
